{
  "stem": "323.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or any of this, or hate, or prejudice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born in Germany, but I'm not a German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I go back to Germany now-- because I have cousins there, from this aunt who was married to a Catholic.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She-- her- her- my uncle died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She still lives there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had five children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The five children are all Catholics, because they had to be baptized and convert when Hitler came, which didn't help them anyhow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my cousin's daughter is leaning towards Judaism now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm very close to this cousin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were first four brothers and one daughter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'm very close to Liesl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, she's coming to the United States and going cross country with me next summer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was with her just recently.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went hiking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when I'm in Germany, I'm not no longer a European.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm an American.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We think differently, we are different, believe me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I'm not a German or a European.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm talking about values now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- I have different values.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I look at things differently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I look at people-- now people my age or younger had-- I can't hate them, I can't-- I can't blame them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of them, they either weren't born or they were small children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I look at some of the older people and I say, gee, I wonder what you were doing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All I can tell you, no one will ever put me anywhere where I don't want to be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, that I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I would fight and die before that would happen again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody knew anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remembered the good days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My early childhood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I went to Hellenthal, my grandfather's house is still there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
